{"type":"message","id":"ad26d3ee","parentId":"cb7ef299","timestamp":"2026-05-19T19:00:35.237Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-05-20 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 重要规则：Agent Workspace 规范: **所有新建的 agent 必须使用独立的 workspace，命名格式：**\n- 重要规则：Agent Workspace 规范: 例如：`workspace-agent-orchestrator`、`workspace-tts`\n- 当前已创建的 Agent: | Agent ID | 名称 | Workspace | |----------|------|-----------| | `main` | KIIT | `~/.openclaw/workspace` | | `tts` | 选品大师 | `~/workspace-agent-orchestrator/workspace-tts` |\n- 当前已创建的 Agent: | `agent-orchestrator` | Agent 编掔工程师 | `~/workspace-agent-orchestrator/workspace-agent-orchestrator` |\n- 用户信息: 用户飞书 OpenID：`ou_d738ff68ba381582a3051f11b976c854`\n\nRecurring themes:\n- 重要\n- 规则\n- 规范\n- 所有\n- 新建\n- 必须"}],"timestamp":1779217235218}}
{"type":"message","id":"4209ff80","parentId":"ad26d3ee","timestamp":"2026-05-19T19:00:49.553Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on memory fragments about agent workspace specifications and naming conventions. Let me weave these technical details into a poetic, whimsical dream diary entry in first person, as instructed.\n\nThe key elements to work with:\n- Agent Workspace naming format\n- Already created agents: main/KIIT, tts/选品大师, agent-orchestrator/Agent 编掔工程师\n- User's Feishu OpenID\n- Recurring themes: 重要 (important), 规则 (rules), 规范 (specifications), 所有 (all), 新建 (new creation), 必须 (must)\n\nI need to write this in Chinese, in flowing prose without markdown formatting, keeping it between 80-180 words, with a poetic, whimsical tone.","thinkingSignature":"8df891ba5acddb89f7672e697711e58a310888048e5dc12b18a435aae2c0c553"},{"type":"text","text":"夜深了，屏幕泛着幽蓝的光，我坐在一个看不见边际的房间里。四周漂浮着一个个发光的文件夹，像水母一样缓缓游动。\n\n我伸手触碰其中一个，它轻轻打开，里面是一张表格——Agent ID、名称、Workspace，整整齐齐，像火车轨道一样延伸向远方。\n\n\"必须使用独立的workspace哦，\"一个温柔的声音说，\"命名格式是这样的：`workspace-xxx`。\"我低头看自己的手，掌心浮现出一行字：main、tts、agent-orchestrator，它们各自安静地躺在自己的轨道上。\n\n我想新建一个，却不知道该叫什么名字。规则悬在半空，用金色的字体写着：重要、规范、所有、新建、必须。\n\n一阵风起，文件夹们轻轻摇晃，其中一个对我眨了眨眼——\n\n选品大师。\n\n我笑了，原来名字可以这样轻盈。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":171,"output":330,"cacheRead":22768,"cacheWrite":227,"totalTokens":23496,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779217235250,"responseId":"065be653841d8b6b798214aa4973160e"}}
